com.pkrete.xrd4j.client.deserializer

Class AbstractResponseDeserializer<T1,T2>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pkrete.xrd4j.common.deserializer.AbstractHeaderDeserializer
      • com.pkrete.xrd4j.client.deserializer.AbstractResponseDeserializer<T1,T2>
  • Type Parameters:
    T1 - runtime type of the request data
    T2 - runtime type of the response data
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ServiceResponseDeserializer

    public abstract class AbstractResponseDeserializer<T1,T2>
extends com.pkrete.xrd4j.common.deserializer.AbstractHeaderDeserializer
implements ServiceResponseDeserializer
    This abstract class serves as a base class for response deserializers. This class offers a method that deserializes SOAP header, but the deserialization of SOAP body's request and response elements must be implemented in the subclasses as their implementation is application specific.

      • deserializeFaultDetail

        protected Object deserializeFaultDetail(Node detailNode)
        Deserializes fault detail element as String. If detail element has child elements all the content of the children is presented as one concatenated String. If detail element has children, this method can be overridden.
        Parameters:
        detailNode - detail element
        Returns:
        detail element's value as string. If detail element is not found, null is returned
